name: Sourpuss Galley Ho Wallet
description:
Sail the seven seas with this black vinyl wallet from Sourpuss!
Anchor pattern with a magnetic closure.

name: Black Mesh Cat Dress
description:
Another variation of the cat dress that is just purrrrfect!
This is in BLACK ONLY but white can be ordered =) The black comes with a black bow, not a white one as pictured.

Recommended for a size 8-12 but also fits a small 14!

Please note, I did not take these pictures. They're just being used until I have time to take my own lol

name: Royal Blue Satin Sleeveless Dress
description:
The dress is made of satin-like fabric, has belt in the waist, slight pleats in the waist and flaring skirt.

This is a size 38 which equates to 8-10
Please check the measurements provided.
All measurements are approximate and should be correct within 1-2cm.

Please note, in the picture the dress is worn with a petticoat to 'poof' it out and I'm thinking about getting some of these in very soon!

name: Mens Sugar Skull Tee
description:
Mens loose fitted Sugar Skull tee by 'Akumu Ink'
These tees are super cool, original designs, all the way from Canada!

Say hello to NZs' first stockist of Akumu Ink!!
'Akumu' is Japanese for 'Nightmare' and all designs are drawn and inspired by Japanese culture, horror movies and pop culture.

name: Too Fast Dead Flamingo Heels
description:
These bad ass dead flamingo open toe heels are a must for any rockers shoe collection!
Featuring skeletal flamingoes with pink wings, this shoe has a faded look AND a super cool 'bone' heel.
I have these in stock in a size 9 and a 10 but...

PLEASE NOTE - I have discovered that Too Fast shoes run slightly larger then regular shoes. If you like your shoes to be tight fitting, I recommend ordering a size down E.G - I am a size 8.5 and wasn't sure on sizing so I ordered a 9 and they are more then .5 too big.
Please contact me if you need more information on shoe sizing for Too Fast =)

name: Too Fast 'Blondie Bandeau' Lingerie Set
description:
This lingerie set from Too Fast is super cute! It features a bandeau top with bow and vinyl skull detail with matching hipster-cut underwear.
Only one set available in a size XL but please check the measurements provided as Too Fast run abit small.

name: Cute Green Cameo Necklace
description: Cute green cameo necklace with little gems at the top of the border! Super long chain too! Get yours!

name: Sourpuss Dainty Mesh Top - Navy
description:
Look instantly put together in the Sourpuss Dotted Dainty top! 
This navy figure flattering top features a delicate heart shaped neckline, decorative center bow, mesh panels & subtle black on navy polka dots.

name: 'Kustom Kreeps' Live Fast, Die Last Tee
description:
Sourpuss Kustom Kreeps "Live Fast...Die Last" t-shirt! The panther on this tee is spittin' mad in dark teal and white and the crossed switchblades and pinstriping bring a rockbilly feel to this tattoo-style tee.

Size M and L available.

name: Sourpuss Tiki Slit Dress
description:
Be someone's Polynesian dream in the Sourpuss Tiki Slit Dress! 
This pink, stretch cotton, curve-hugging dress features 2 decorative buttons, adjustable straps, removable stretch belt and 2 revealing slits up the front.

name: Sourpuss Swallow Waist Belt
description:
Dress up any outfit with our Sourpuss Vintage Sparrow Belt! This stretchy black cinch belt has a faux leather cutout of a sparrow in the center. Each belt has 3 silver snaps for perfect fit every time!

Size XL

name: Pink BARBIE Necklace
description:
Cute pink necklace for the 'doll' in your life!
Approximately 7cm and comes on a silver chain.
3 available!

name: Red Cherry Lashes #5
description:
Dramatic style Red Cherry false lashes.
100% human hair. Made to look natural and blend with your own eyelashes.
These are super soft and can be re-used if looked after.

name: 'Trust No Bitch' Necklace
description:
Don't trust bitches?.. Then this badass necklace is for you!
Adjustable chain for the perfect length!

name: Kustom Kreeps Kiss of Death
description:
A tattooed, decomposing cutie adorns this short-sleeve, guys' black tee in red, white and gray print. 
The banners read, "Kustom Kreeps...Kiss of Death".

name: Kustom Kreeps Lady Luck Tee
description:
Get lucky in this tee from Kustom Kreeps! 
This short-sleeve, black t-shirt features Lady Luck, herself, surrounded by flames, dice, stars and "Lady Luck" text above her head.

name: Sourpuss Sinking Ship Blue Dress
description:
Sinking clipper ships and nautical compasses make up the pattern on this amazing deep sea-blue fabric. 
The Bella dress has a great fit, with a smocked back, cute cuffed sleeves and button front. 
Made of stretch cotton.

name: Cotton Polka Dot Halter Top
description:
Glamorous pin-up 50's style halter top, polka dot stretch cotton fabric with a side zip. So fitting and elegant!

I have this in a 42 and a 44 which equates to a 14 and a 16.
Please check the measurements!

name: Eyeball Necklace-Single Strand
description: Creepy but cool eyeball necklace, single strand with 5 eyes and long chain.

name: Champagne Bracelet Ring Combo
description:
This bracelet and ring combo is just gorgeous!
Both the bracelet AND the ring are adjustable.

name: Zombie Hand Necklace
description:
Zombie hand necklace available in an assortment of colours!!
If I don't have the colour you're after, please ask because there is about 20 different ones!!

These are really awesome, unleash your inner zombie!!!
